    "This comparative analysis is intended to furnish diverse insights and formative experiences, contributing significantly to the ongoing discourse on the role and impact of large language models in healthcare research.",
    "Our study illustrates the marked variability in the performance of different large language models when processing real-world medical scenario information.",
    "The objective of our research is not solely to compare and rank these models but to emphasize the adaptability and potential of LLMs in the medical field.",
    "This realization underscores the necessity of careful and precise benchmarking tailored for medical AI applications.",
    "We have also discovered that specific fine-tuning and alignment of LLMs significantly enhance their ability to perform specialized tasks within the medical domain, even on smaller-scale models."
